%F A376467 T(n, k) = Sum_{j = k..n} binomial(n, j)*binomial(n+j, j)*binomial(j, k).
%F A376467 (n - k)*T(n, k) = 3*(2*n - 1)*T(n-1, k) - (n + k - 1)*T(n-2, k).
